title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 27 2015 Tue.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton OCT 27 2015 Tue (03:07:52)

On Today's Show:

PETE DAVIDSON, STANLEY TUCCI.

They talk about hassles they had trying to watch the movie "Spotlight" last night and then they go on to talk about the movie itself. Jimmy talks about buying naked pics from a girl. They talk about Mike Tyson yesterday and some political correctness in Halloween stuff.

Pete Davidson joins them and they talk about Mike Tyson. They talk about Donald Trump, a new report about bacon and other meats causing cancer, news about a guy found with thousands of guns, and Pete attacks Justin.

Justin is attacked some more and it's brought up that he and his brother will be leaving the show in several months to work on a new TV show. They get into talking about Catholic Priests.

Stanley Tucci joins them and they talk about his new movie, Spotlight, about Catholic Priests in Boston, and they talk about some other things
